title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today’s Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the new PGA event headed by Tiger and Rory. Plus, he talks to Brian Windhorst about the Nets chances of winning a title and the possibility of the Lakers moving on from Russ Westbrook.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
